表格职工表的代码预览

drop index Relationship_3_FK on user;

drop index Relationship_2_FK on user;

drop index Relationship_1_FK on user;

drop index user_PK on user;

drop table if exists user;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: user */
/*==============================================================*/
create table user
(
user_id int character set utf8 not null auto_increment,
artisan_id int,
artisan_set_id int,
post_id int,
user_name varchar(10),
user_pwd varchar(10),
user_date date,
user_address varchar(100),
user_educ varchar(20),
user_school varchar(30),
user_entry date,
user_dimiss date,
user_pay float,
user_status varchar(10),
user_store2 varchar(20),
user_store3 varchar(30),
user_store4 varchar(40),
user_store1 varchar(10),
primary key (user_id)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: user_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index user_PK on user
(
user_id
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Relationship_1_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index Relationship_1_FK on user
(
post_id
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Relationship_2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index Relationship_2_FK on user
(
artisan_id
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: Relationship_3_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index Relationship_3_FK on user
(
artisan_set_id
);

alter table user add constraint FK_Relationship_1 foreign key (post_id)
references post (post_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table user add constraint FK_Relationship_2 foreign key (artisan_id)
references 技工星级表 (artisan_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table user add constraint FK_Relationship_3 foreign key (artisan_set_id)
references artisan_set (artisan_set_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
